headline: Paycom Software, Inc. Announces Fourth Quarter and Year-End 2025 Earnings Release Date and Conference Call
summary: OKLAHOMA CITY, January 21, 2026--Paycom Software, Inc. ("Paycom") (NYSE: PAYC), a leading provider of comprehensive, cloud-based human capital management software, will release its results for the fourth quarter and year-ended Dec. 31, 2025, after the market closes on Feb. 11. Paycom will also hold a conference call to discuss results at 5 p.m. (Eastern) that day.

headline: National Duals Invitational Adds $150,000 to 2026 Prize Purse
summary: OKLAHOMA CITY, January 21, 2026--The National Duals Invitational, a groundbreaking collegiate wrestling event sponsored by Paycom, generated more than $180,000 in net proceeds in 2025, all of which will be allocated to the 2026 prize purse and additional event advertising.

headline: Software Stocks: From Market Leaders to AI Victims
summary: After a decade of growth and soaring stock prices, the software industry is being disrupted by artificial intelligence.
